                me \lim_{\im z\to \infty} G_k(z) = \lim_{\im z\to \infty} \sum'_{m,n\in \ZZ} \frac{1}{(mz+n)^k} = \sum'_{n\in \ZZ} \frac{1}{n^k} = 2\zeta(k)
